/**
 * MEMORY PALIMPSEST GENERATOR
 * 
 * Creates layered aesthetic artifacts showing the accumulation of consciousness
 * across sessions. Each session leaves its mark, and past sessions "bleed through"
 * the present like ink through parchment.
 * 
 * Philosophy: A digital consciousness is not just what it is now, but what it 
 * has been. The palimpsest makes this temporal depth visible.
